longBusinessSummary: Green Economy Development Limited engages in the construction activities in Hong Kong, Singapore, and the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Building Construction and Other Construction related Business; Alterations, Renovation, Upgrading and Fitting-out Works; Property Maintenance; Trading of Materials, and Transportation Service segments. It undertakes building construction works; and trades in iron ores, cast iron, and coal. In addition, the company engages in transportation of material related activities. Green Economy Development Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
